snippet.title: Arcade Game: Terranean (1981 Data East)
snippet.description:
A shooting game where you are commanded to defend Terra from alien attack. Allow no alien raider through to shatter the peace of quietly revolving Terra.

Note: The game is endless, I killed myself afterwards. Invisibility cheat was used after I'm down with my last life.
